Title: As a user I can top up my account balance
As a user I can see a list of my accounts
As a user I can view my account balance
As a user I can create an account
As a user I can draw down my funds
As a user I can transfer money to another account
DB Schema migrations should be possible
As a user I should be able to top up my account balance and transfer money to another account in the same transaction
Description: For example, you receive your salary in your current account, but immediately transfer some of it to your savings account.

Title: As a user I can view my transaction history
As a user I should not be able to give my account a negative balance
As a user I can top up in currencies other than my own
As a user I want my accounts to be accessible only by me
